8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: Maugan's Folly used to be a Zakarum fort, a foothold for our efforts. But It was lost generations ago.

CEC9D6D4.Line17.121C9F: But it didn't go as they had hoped. Some returned, wounded. Some, like my master, did not return at all. If you hadn't helped me, her name would have been lost forever.

DF0D9F2A.VoiceDir1.121C9F: Flat. Educational. Pushing feelings aside. The memory is fresh, but you don't show it.

F6462D12.Line15.121C9F: My master, Johanna, gathered a group of crusaders to take it back. To begin our trek back into the swamp in search of Akarat. But...
